title: CEO of DuckDuckGo Testifies in Google Case
description: Gabriel Weinberg of the search engine DuckDuckGo was the first competitor to testify in the Justice Department’s antitrust trial against Google.

title: Rupert Murdoch to Retire From Fox and News Corporation Boards
description: The move leaves his son Lachlan as the sole executive in charge of the global media empire.

title: The Lawyers Sam Bankman-Fried Once Trusted Are Drawing Criticism
description: Mr. Bankman-Fried and his allies have blasted Sullivan & Cromwell, the New York law firm managing FTX’s bankruptcy, for its tangled relationship with the crypto exchange.
